            <h3 class="heading-tertiary text-secondary-dark mb-4">Commercial Excavation Contractor</h3>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-6">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-orange">$320,000</div>
              <div class="text-gray-600 font-semibold">Equipment Finance Package</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="space-y-6">
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-secondary-dark font-semibold mb-2">Business Background</h4>
                <p class="body-medium text-gray-700">Established excavation and earthmoving contractor serving commercial construction projects across South East Queensland. 8-year track record with consistent revenue growth and strong client relationships with major construction companies.</p>
              </div>
              
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-secondary-dark font-semibold mb-2">Challenge</h4>
                <p class="body-medium text-gray-700">Contractor identified significant opportunity to expand operations with larger commercial projects requiring additional heavy machinery. Traditional bank financing proved inadequate for specialised equipment requirements.</p>
              </div>
              
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-secondary-dark font-semibold mb-2">Solution</h4>
