            <div class="bg-secondary-dark text-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold mb-4 inline-block">Equipment Finance</div>
            <h3 class="heading-tertiary text-secondary-dark mb-4">Steel Fabrication Business</h3>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-6">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-orange">$450,000</div>
              <div class="text-gray-600 font-semibold">Industrial Equipment Finance</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="space-y-6">
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-secondary-dark font-semibold mb-2">Business Background</h4>
                <p class="body-medium text-gray-700">Specialised steel fabrication company serving mining and industrial sectors. 12-year operational history with focus on custom fabrication and maintenance services for heavy industry.</p>
              </div>
              
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-secondary-dark font-semibold mb-2">Challenge</h4>
                <p class="body-medium text-gray-700">Growing demand for precision manufacturing required investment in CNC machinery and automated welding systems. Existing equipment limiting capacity to meet client requirements and quality standards.</p>
              </div>
              
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-secondary-dark font-semibold mb-2">Solution</h4>
                <p class="body-medium text-gray-700">Strategic equipment finance for advanced manufacturing capability including CNC plasma cutting system, automated welding cells, and precision measurement equipment with technology refresh provisions.</p>
              </div>
              
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-secondary-dark font-semibold mb-3">Outcome</h4>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-4">
                  <div class="text-center card-padding-sm bg-neutral-light rounded-lg">
                    <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-orange">65%</div>
                    <div class="text-xs text-gray-600">Production efficiency gain</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="text-center card-padding-sm bg-neutral-light rounded-lg">
                    <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-orange">$320K</div>
